data.description: Not your typical Split Foyer! This updated 4-bedroom, 2 ½ bath home offers w/2200+ sq. ft of finished space (per owner). You will love the terrific open floor plan & the spaciousness of the rooms; as you enter the main floor with all engineered Hardwood; big Great Rm open to white Kitchen w/newer SS appliances plenty of counter space & a big dining area. Three beds on the main floor with an updated full bath. The lower level showcases a impressive family room with a beautiful wood burning fireplace, a spacious primary bdrm w/a spa-like bath and walkin closet. There is also a half bath & laundry room. A deck on the east side provides sunshine in the morning & afternoon plus shade in the evening. The fenced yd is not only a safe haven for children & pets but also a perfect for outdoor activities. Whether hosting summer barbecues, gardening or simply basking in the sunshine, the yard becomes an extension of the home's charm. Located in the heart of Ankeny, it is close to parks, backs to NW Elementary School & close to uptown amenities; plus a block or so from jumping on the the Trestle Trail bike trail. You can enjoy the convenience of easy access to recreational spaces for outdoor activities & the vibrancy of uptown living, including shopping, dining & entertainment options; schools, Saylorville & easy access to I-35 and I-80. This home's appeal is in seamlessly combining comfort, style & convenience. An exceptional home at an exceptional value.
